  "bio_raw": "Barrister Nafia Haque is a Lecturer of the ULAB School of Business. She has 04 years’ teaching experience under the University of London (Bachelor of Laws) (International Programmes) curriculum and has been teaching at the University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh from 2025 till date. She has taken courses related to law within the scope of businesses, including Contract Law, Company Law, Trade Finance etc. She has also taken Introductory Business courses and courses related to International Business.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Contract Law, Company Law, Trade Finance, International Business, Introduction to Business."
  ],
  "education": [
    {
      "raw": "Education\nBar Vocational Studies (BVS) (2023), The City Law School, University of London, UK.\nMaster of Laws (LLM) (Masters) (2022), The City Law School, University of London, UK.\nBachelor of Laws (LLB) (Hons) (2021), Department of Law, University of London (International Programmes)."
    }
  ],
